{"tid":992361,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"EA足球遊戲為沙拿增添「插水」特質","createTime":"2019-01-23T06:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T12:05:11.000Z","uid":147522,"like":298,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"f0aa6ca881a06e4685513844487e7face2b9359e","tid":992361,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"　　FIFA系列遊戲會隨著現實球員的實時動態更新遊戲裡球員的屬性以反映真實的性能。在上週末紅軍4-3戰勝水晶宮的比賽中，這位埃及球星攻入兩球，他曾在禁區內跟前紅軍後衛沙高的一次對抗中倒地，兩隊還為此發生了些小衝突。在賽後，沙拿被指控插水。<br />\n<br />\n　　EA體育公司現在已經介入了這場辯論，並給沙拿更新了「插水」的特質。EA 體育將這一特點描述為：「具有這一特點的球員更容易在最小接觸下倒下。」<br />\n<br />\n　　沙拿此前已經有了反越位，精準射門，以及其本身的球員特點。同時他的12碼屬性也有了很大的提升，從61升到了75。"},{"pid":"0be3442deead8d9de9a746cfa83134b9dbc286c3","tid":992361,"uid":11254,"like":77,"dislike":11,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:13:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母EA SPORT"},{"pid":"4676ac206f9200d391998b7a29948fc7bd25fe2a","tid":992361,"uid":143288,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cd3e9d211bd12019e3c49a431501588df939e7","tid":992361,"uid":124891,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"Ea撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5220014152501b95155ff4bffc689f98c822101","tid":992361,"uid":34572,"like":150,"dislike":2,"score":148,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母拉莫斯！"},{"pid":"3d0632b2cd84b3ec4d20f85a7012e42eb1bd3280","tid":992361,"uid":58303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n